    "Additionally, to maintain the original image dimensions, any empty spaces resulting from the data augmentation procedures were filled with black pixels.",
    "Visual illustrations of the input images following the application of the data augmentation procedures are presented in Fig. 1.",
    "The ResNet network architecture includes preprocessing layers, and residual units, as well as a fully connected layer and a Softmax layer.",
    "The key innovation of ResNet resides in its incorporation of residual connectivity, which effectively addresses the challenges of gradient vanishing and exploding encountered during the training of deep networks, by establishing direct interconnections between layers.",
